 />\n望下法輪功 人地捱左幾十年都無放棄到仲地球度度都有 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dc57e8a0d8f3d7c2724711749a5d181f634adfe9","tid":2358635,"uid":87511,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-08T09:41:58.000Z","msg":"做一同二點都好過做三<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"663c836182d2a2a27ae1c99b6a1e6a2ffa3f6183","tid":2358635,"uid":31215,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"e390496f469a1b1e1c2d9e33fd5615112272940c","tid":2358635,"uid":42804,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-08T09:39:19.000Z","msg":"第三類人好易會變成熱狗或深藍<br />\n因為當佢哋習慣放棄自己，將社會嘅不滿發洩落其他人身上，結果只會鑽牛角尖，越走越遠，甚至變成為利益而攻擊黃絲。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-08T09:42:12.000Z","msg":"五毛都好鍾意扮第三類<br />\n成日串柒第一類<br />\n搞到第一類而家有少少神經質聽到呢啲留言就好易屈毛"},{"pid":"5f08889421c149d207389ccc3c2f7a45546b4324","tid":2358635,"uid":87511,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"aa187dac66c3603ecb8032043f9ddf3469f3aebc","tid":2358635,"uid":69221,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-08T09:39:26.000Z","msg":"行動撚喺真正戰場上俾人捉鬼捉左兩年，心灰意冷退落黎上連登Bin C/做假膠<br />\n<br />\n鍵盤戰士捉左兩年鬼，仲當緊網上係戰場，捉啲假想敵黎屈毛屈熱<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/pray.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"x-small\">Lm等趕盡殺絕入黎</span>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-08T09:44:10.000Z","msg":"亂鳩咁嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n你可以話部分灰心撚當係畀人捉鬼捉咗好多次，但係唔係個個灰心撚都畀人捉鬼<br />\n<br />\n咪混淆試聽"},{"pid":"4727bd48a6de732cb7271f0e023d42671318d7e3","tid":2358635,"uid":31215,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"dc57e8a0d8f3d7c2724711749a5d181f634adfe9","tid":2358635,"uid":87511,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-08T09:41:58.000Z","msg":"做一同二點都好過做三<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0